      <title>瑞典呼吁北欧国家共同努力阻止枪支犯罪蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sweden-calls-for-nordic-effort-to-stop-gun-crime-from-spreading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典司法部长 Gunnar Strommer 在丹麦发生一系列瑞典人暴力犯罪事件后表示，瑞典将与北欧地区的政府和当局合作，防止帮派暴力蔓延到境外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sweden-calls-for-nordic-effort-to-stop-gun-crime-from-spreading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国怀疑俄罗斯参与破坏军事基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-suspects-russian-hand-in-sabotage-at-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柏林一位资深议员称，德国正在调查俄罗斯可能对两个军事基地实施的破坏行为，据称有人试图污染饮用水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-suspects-russian-hand-in-sabotage-at-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦考虑征收商品出口税以缩小预算缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kazakhstan-may-tax-metals-commodities-exports-seeking-more-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，哈萨克斯坦今年正考虑对金属和燃料等原材料出口征税，以帮助弥补预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kazakhstan-may-tax-metals-commodities-exports-seeking-more-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非称铁路公司业绩不佳导致失业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/transnet-south-africa-rebukes-rail-monopoly-over-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府严厉批评了经营国有货运铁路垄断业务的 Transnet SOC 有限公司的糟糕表现，称其导致这个三分之一失业的国家失去了就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/transnet-south-africa-rebukes-rail-monopoly-over-performance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士推动提高增值税以增加养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/swiss-government-pushes-for-vat-increase-to-fund-pension-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府表示，为支持最近决定的养老金上调，政府倾向于增加国家增值税，而不是提高工资缴款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/swiss-government-pushes-for-vat-increase-to-fund-pension-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 12:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里兰拒绝土耳其结束索马里与埃塞俄比亚裂痕的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/somaliland-rebuffs-turkey-s-bid-to-end-somalia-ethiopia-standoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里的分离地区索马里兰誓言推进将部分领土租给埃塞俄比亚的有争议的计划，并批评土耳其为调解该交易僵局所做的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/somaliland-rebuffs-turkey-s-bid-to-end-somalia-ethiopia-standoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院裁定总理在道德案件中罪名成立，将其免职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院裁定总理斯雷塔·塔维辛违反道德规范，解除其职务，这导致这个东南亚国家陷入新一轮的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰声称军队正在推进，俄罗斯抵抗无人机攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/russia-shot-down-117-drones-in-one-of-largest-overnight-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯称，其防空部队击落了 117 架无人机和 4 枚战术导弹，这是战争期间最大规模的夜间袭击之一，而乌克兰军队则声称继续向俄罗斯领土推进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/russia-shot-down-117-drones-in-one-of-largest-overnight-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑采取罕见的反垄断举措：拆分谷歌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/doj-considers-seeking-google-goog-breakup-after-major-antitrust-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在一项具有里程碑意义的法庭裁决认定谷歌垄断了在线搜索市场后，拆分谷歌是美国司法部正在考虑的选项之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/doj-considers-seeking-google-goog-breakup-after-major-antitrust-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球移民打击行动使留学生陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际学生 — — 长期以来一直是发达经济体高校的摇钱树 — — 面临着越来越不确定的未来，因为各国政府都在寻求简单的目标来控制激增的移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
